Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.86,0:33:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I almost forgave the bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.73,0:33:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.78,0:33:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can count on you to tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.99,0:33:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\NI'm on your side, Miwa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.41,0:33:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still in the studio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.91,0:33:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.83,0:33:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I went a little too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.71,0:33:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I don't go to these extremes,\Nthere's no chance for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.09,0:33:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.21,0:33:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.67,0:33:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I cleared up the misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.59,0:33:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's actually kind of pissed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She was like, "Why did he take me back\Nto his place and not do anything to me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.60,0:33:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Most girls would have that expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.35,0:33:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Men are like that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And she sort of expected it, you retard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.48,0:33:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was really mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.65,0:33:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't really know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.24,0:33:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You re really a nitwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.95,0:33:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme tell ya about women.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.95,0:33:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They act the exact opposite\Nof the way they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.12,0:34:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s only acting embarrassed and mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.78,0:34:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's the opposite. Opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.91,0:34:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Women sure are complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.46,0:34:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.00,0:34:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.71,0:34:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't understand how you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you grin at me like\Na hungry five-year-old?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.72,0:34:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even worse than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You say I was the one who\Ncame on to you? You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.06,0:34:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I come on to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.02,0:34:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't ever want to see your face again!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.73,0:34:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I don't really\Nunderstand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.94,0:34:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is that also the opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.57,0:34:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.91,0:34:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, like, that you want to sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.58,0:34:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You dirty worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.75,0:34:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, was I stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.46,0:34:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I really shouldn't trust men.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.71,0:34:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.34,0:34:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't get women!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.56,0:35:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With cheap money, you tried\Nto change our video?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.90,0:35:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where did all this money come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.24,0:35:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Koganei Junpei and Director\NMiwa, "Love Angel" was a big success.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.62,0:35:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the look on that octopus’s face?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.38,0:35:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miwa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.30,0:35:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The octopus of the adult film\Nindustry was just here.
