Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.51,0:35:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Resignation?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.93,0:35:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.81,0:35:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting Apollo Productions after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.36,0:35:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.52,0:35:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.86,0:35:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.78,0:36:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could keep my personal\Nlife and work separate,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.70,0:36:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't work with someone\NI don't respect as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.74,0:36:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.75,0:36:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.81,0:36:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.91,0:36:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.71,0:36:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.21,0:36:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.13,0:36:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.89,0:36:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.89,0:36:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.48,0:36:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's both have some fun while we're in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.64,0:36:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.23,0:36:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see no problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.44,0:36:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already done it once before, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.90,0:36:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.57,0:36:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't make a difference\Nif we fuck a few more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.65,0:36:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.36,0:36:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.57,0:36:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you'll win in a fight against a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.66,0:36:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
